➜把「风属性」点满的戴森，是如何玩转气流的
https://www.ifanr.com/1373010?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	11705
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373061" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/title2.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/title2.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/title2-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/title2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/title2-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>不知各位记不记得，在一些美剧或欧美电影里，偶尔能看到一种下面挂着个大袋子，后面还拖着条长长的电源线的吸尘器，就如下图所展示的那样，又笨又重。</p>
<p>今天再看到这种古早的尘袋式吸尘器，会给人一种「干家务活真累」的感觉。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373011" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Kirby.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1777" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Kirby.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Kirby-360x640.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Kirby-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Kirby-576x1024.jpg 576w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.pinterest.com/pin/342836590360346397/">Pinterest</a></p>
</div>
<p>不过我好奇的是，吸尘器是如何从袋鼠一般的形态，进化到如今单手便可操作的无绳形态的呢？</p>
<p>我在 10 月 20 日的戴森技术沉浸体验日活动中，找到了答案。</p>
<h3>打破传统，人类迎来了无线吸尘时代</h3>
<p>上面提到的尘袋式吸尘器，诞生于上世纪初，所谓的「大袋子」其实是装有过滤网的集尘袋，它又大又累赘，使用一段时间后还会出现堵塞的状况，清理麻烦，吸力也会随之降低。</p>
<p>正当用户都对这种缺陷感觉苦恼时，就到了「天降勐男」的时刻，这位「勐男」便是戴森品牌创始人詹姆斯戴森。</p>
<p>平日喜爱发明的他，看着家里「又双叒叕」坏掉的吸尘器，打算自己改造一下，从工业锯木厂中用来分离木屑的气旋分离器中获得了灵感，并将气流技术应用到吸尘器当中。</p>
<p>经过 N 次试验后，戴森于 1982 年首先使用气旋分离技术并运用到全球第一台无尘袋气旋式吸尘器的原型样机上，这款原型有个响亮的名字，「G-Force」。</p>
<p>戴森在原型机的基础上进一步改进了气旋技术，于 1993 年推出了搭载双气旋技术的 DC01 吸尘器，当时定价是竞品的两倍，看来戴森的贵是「历史遗留问题」了，但洁净力和吸力都比其他产品更强，所以 DC01 上市之后，便成为当时英国最畅销的吸尘器。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373012" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01204.jpg" alt="" width="1162" height="1743" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01204.jpg 1162w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01204-360x540.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01204-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01204-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1162px) 100vw, 1162px" /></p>
<p>从那时开始，戴森算是跟气流技术杠上了。</p>
<h3>埋头深造，气流也能玩出多种花样</h3>
<p>后来的戴森，接连在气旋技术、数码马达、气流倍增技术（Air Amplifier）等创新领域取得突破，这些技术在今天体验日中均有展出。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373022" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01216.jpg" alt="" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01216.jpg 1800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01216-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01216-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01216-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲右边是戴森的数码马达</p>
</div>
<p>以气流倍增技术为例，这项创新如今被应用到戴森旗下多款产品上，最为人所熟知的便是它的无叶风扇。</p>
<p>从这台无叶风扇的剖面可以看出，气流在环状气流腔体中循环，透过狭缝被加速吹出，由弧形翼面引导气流的喷射方向。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373013" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01207.jpg" alt="" width="1254" height="836" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01207.jpg 1254w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01207-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01207-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01207-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373014" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/air.gif" alt="" width="1000" height="562" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/air.gif 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/air-360x202.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/air-768x432.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲远距离送风</p>
</div>
<p>于是得以呈现出安全无叶的形态，在体验上则没有了传统风扇直送风所带来的不适感。这项气流倍增技术也被应用到戴森 Supersonic 吹风机中，这款「吹风机界的爱马仕」打破了传统吹风机的设计样式，以新奇的使用体验吸引了许多少女的心。</p>
<p>在现场体验区可以清晰看到，戴森 Supersonic 吹风机吹出的气流能够让小球稳定的悬浮在空中，这证明了它吹出的气流非常均匀，从而可以做到快速干发而不伤发。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373015" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind.gif" alt="" width="1000" height="562" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind.gif 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind-360x202.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind-768x432.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>现场展示的另一款戴森 Pure Cool Me 净化风扇也很有意思，戴森在鹞式战斗机的空气动力学特性启发下，发明了 Core Flow 气流聚合技术并且运用到这款风扇上。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373016" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01212.jpg" alt="" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01212.jpg 1800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01212-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01212-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01212-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲调节球面，指哪打哪</p>
</div>
<p>戴森 Pure Cool Me 净化风扇同样无叶，但形态上与前面所展示的无叶风扇有明显差异。前者的顶部有一个球，气流从底部吹出，沿着球面喷射出来，四周的气流正在圆顶相遇时，下方形成高压，于是在这个高压点的影响下，气流被迫喷射出聚集的气流。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373018" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/pcm.png" alt="" width="1120" height="739" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/pcm.png 1120w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/pcm-360x238.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/pcm-768x507.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/pcm-1024x676.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1120px) 100vw, 1120px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>图片来源：戴森</p>
</div>
<p>鹞式战斗机利用这个原理实现了垂直升降，而戴森则用它造了个有趣的风扇。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373079" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Harrier.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="868" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Harrier.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Harrier-360x244.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Harrier-768x521.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Harrier-1024x694.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>图片来源：<a href="http://www.wikiwand.com/zh/%E6%B5%B7%E9%B9%9E%E6%88%98%E6%96%97%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E6%9C%BA">wikiwand</a></p>
</div>
<p>接着往前走，我们看到了这个白色房间，里面立着许多细柱，细柱上是绑着空气检测仪，房间角落放着戴森 HP06 空气净化风扇。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373019" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/room.jpg" alt="" width="1322" height="991" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/room.jpg 1322w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/room-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/room-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/room-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1322px) 100vw, 1322px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373020" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01238.jpg" alt="" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01238.jpg 1800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01238-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01238-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01238-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<blockquote><p>27 平米，是中国大多数家庭客厅的大小。</p></blockquote>
<p>这是戴森工程师经过调研后得出的结论。</p>
<p>他们独创了 POLAR（Point Loading Auto Response）实验方法，并专门造出了这个 27 平米大的房间，用来检测自家净化风扇能否做到均匀净化。若分布在不同位置的检测仪，读数近乎一致，说明达到了理想的效果。</p>
<p>我在这一场体验日活动里，看到了戴森众多产品线，及其背后技术原理的直观展示。</p>
<p>在这些技术背后是 6000 多名工程师和科学家的持续专研。</p>
<p>了解过后才会明白，戴森产品之所以相较同类竞品更贵，并不是奢侈品般的品牌溢价，而是保持长久研发活力所需的必要成本。</p>
<h3>创新不止，现在的戴森不只会玩「风」了</h3>
<p>目前戴森市售的产品，譬如吸尘器、和吹风机、空气净化风扇和美发造型器，基本上都是围绕着「气流」在做文章。</p>
<p>而未来的戴森还会在固态电池、数码马达、视觉系统、机器学习及人工智能等多个领域继续发力。</p>
<p>在展馆最末端的家居场景中，摆放着一款台灯，这是戴森最新的 Lightcycle 台灯。因为体验日主题是「劲·流」，讲的都是与气流相关的概念，所以现场并没有关于这款台灯技术的演示内容，它只是作为场景展示品被放在那里。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1373023" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01230.jpg" alt="" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01230.jpg 1800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01230-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01230-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01230-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<p>它静静地伫立在角落，独自发亮，这款由戴森创始人儿子，杰克戴森设计的台灯，或许会成为戴森未来新的里程碑产品，引领着这个品牌在更多的领域推出创新产品。</p>
<p>题图来源：戴森</p>
➜OPPO Find X2 英雄联盟 S10 限定版图赏：够精致，够惊喜
https://www.ifanr.com/1372183?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	12024
<p>近年来手机厂商推出联盟限定版产品似乎成为新的潮流，有和汽车品牌联名的、也有和知名动漫 IP 联名、又或是和知名时尚设计师合作的。而这次我们收到的，是一款和游戏 IP 联名的手机——OPPO Find X2 英雄联盟 S10 限定版。</p>
<p>从开箱到试玩，整个过程中我听到最多的话就是「哇哦，有点酷」。是的，我被一群英雄联盟玩家包围了，从他们的反应来看，这台限定版手机在设计上的确是用心了。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372197" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00981.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00981.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00981-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00981-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00981-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>毕竟如今的手机，要赢得用户真诚的赞叹，可并不容易。</p>
<h3>从包装到手机，满满的 LOL 感</h3>
<p>首先还是来看套装中的手机，这次英雄联盟 S10 限定版可谓是从包装到手机，都是下足了功夫，从运输箱到手机，随处可见英雄联盟 S10 赛事以及游戏内容的定制元素。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372187" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00738.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00738.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00738-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00738-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00738-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>打开运输箱，呈现在我们眼前的是一个方方正正的包装盒，如果你是一位英雄联盟玩家，可能会对这个包装盒产生一种熟悉感，它整体的造型和英雄联盟游戏中的宝箱十分相似。</p>
<p>只不过箱体元素改为了 S10 赛事 logo 和主题曲《Take Over》等，蓝金撞色的设计一看就是为了匹配英雄联盟的游戏地图风格，设计精致程度和观感都较为不错。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372189" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00749.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00749.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00749-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00749-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00749-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>在游戏中，用钥匙打开宝箱，是一件很有仪式感的事，一个宝箱开出来的既有可能是限定皮肤、英雄，也可能游戏中的金币——蓝色精粹和黄色精粹。</p>
<p>也因此，开宝箱是一件让人情绪高扬的事，和我现在打开 OPPO Find X2 英雄联盟 S10 限定版是一样的。</p>
<p>往上轻轻一提就可以打开包装箱，阻尼不会太大，算是推出式包装盒中阻尼比较合适的。接下来就是手机盒了，这个盒子表面倒是没做太多专属设计，同样是加入了英雄联盟 S10 主题曲《TAKE OVER》元素。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372190" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00755.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00755.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00755-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00755-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00755-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>值得注意的是，在打开手机盒的同时，手机也会缓缓上升，和影视剧中宝物在机关的推动下自动上升的结构类似，这个巧妙的设计赢得了我身旁几位朋友的欢呼，看起来确实有点酷。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372191" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00775.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00775.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00775-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00775-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00775-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>手机先暂时放在一边，先来看看手机盒里还有啥。在固定手机的纸板两侧分别有两张卡，一张装着手机卡针，作为一位英雄联盟玩家，这个卡针造型我再熟悉不过了，正是游戏中的视野眼饰品。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372192" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00816.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00816.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00816-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00816-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00816-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>另一张卡则是一张纪念卡，文字 ONE OF 3000 标志着英雄联盟 S10 限定版一共 3000 套。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372194" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00848.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00848.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00848-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00848-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00848-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>拿开固定纸板，就是充电器、充电线、手机壳和定制耳机了，充电器采用了和包装盒一样的黄蓝撞色设计，和英雄联盟游戏中的货币——蓝色、黄色精粹类似。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372193" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00879.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2002" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00879.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00879-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00879-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00879-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>和普通版 OPPO Find X2 一样，英雄联盟 S10 限定版充电器支持 OPPO SuperVOOC 2.0 闪充，最高支持 65W，根据 OPPO 的介绍，4200 mAh 的电池不到 10 分钟就能充至 40% 电量。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372195" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00852.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2002" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00852.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00852-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00852-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00852-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>耳机是入耳式，耳机头部有英雄联盟标志和 S10 赛事主题曲《TAKE OVER》标志。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372196" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00967.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00967.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00967-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00967-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00967-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>接下来看看手机，照例还是简单介绍下手机配置，基本和普通 OPPO Find X2 一致：</p>
<ul>
<li>屏幕：6.7 英寸，3168*1440 分辨率，120Hz 刷新率 OLED 屏幕</li>
<li>SoC：高通骁龙 865</li>
<li>存储组合：8+256GB</li>
<li>成像配置：4800 万像素广角 + 1200 万像素超广角 + 1300 万长焦+3200 万前置</li>
<li>5G：支持</li>
</ul>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372211" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00853.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2002" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00853.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00853-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00853-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00853-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>点亮手机屏幕，展现在眼前的就是游戏中的英雄伊泽瑞尔，而且还和 PC 端游戏英雄页面一样，是以类似动图的形式展现，此外还可以选择李青、乐芙兰、艾瑞莉娅、泰坦共五位英雄的壁纸。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372198" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00820.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00820.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00820-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00820-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00820-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>手机图标基本上都和英雄联盟游戏中出现过的元素相关，像书城图标就来自于游戏装备恶魔法典，值得一提的是不仅仅是 OPPO 自带的系统应用适配了图标，像淘宝、腾讯视频等第三方应用也适配了图标。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372200" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00859.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00859.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00859-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00859-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00859-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>翻到手机背面，整个背面采用了蓝金配色的设计，S10 赛事奖杯标志在手机的正中间，搭配一个雾状的白色标志，和英雄联盟地图中的暗影迷雾还挺像。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372199" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00871.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00871.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00871-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00871-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00871-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>办公室内的几位英雄联盟玩家，把玩过这台 OPPO Find X2 英雄联盟 S10 限定版后，得出的结论倒是蛮一致的：有内味了。</p>
<h3>阿卡丽！阿卡丽！</h3>
<p>相比手机，OPPO Watch 英雄联盟限定版的包装相对会更简单一些，但也能看到不少 OPPO 在联名设计上的传承。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372201" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00893.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00893.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00893-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00893-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00893-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>例如 OPPO Watch 英雄联盟限定版封套表面的阿卡丽浮雕，此前在 OPPO Watch EVA 限定版中也有类似的设计，这种设计的好处是凸出质感，浮雕在不同光影条件展出不同的效果，实际观感提升了不少。</p>
<p>包装盒采用的绿色色调设计也和游戏中阿卡丽的服饰颜色相匹配。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372210" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00902.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00902.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00902-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00902-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00902-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>而且这次 OPPO 对封条设计也进行了改良，除了「一次性封条」设计，也提供了普通的开盒设计，让用户可以在拆封条提升开箱感和最完成的收纳状态中选择，喜爱收藏可以选择普通开箱方式，想提升开箱仪式感就拆「一次性封条」。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372202" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00896.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00896.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00896-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00896-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00896-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>打开封套之后就是包装盒本体了，同样是在限定版包装中常见的礼盒设计，左边是阿卡丽浮雕，右边则是《英雄联盟》logo 等元素，轻轻一提礼盒上露出的绿色丝带，就能打开包装盒了。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372203" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00898.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2002" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00898.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00898-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00898-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00898-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>打开盒子就是手表本体了，用于固定手表的黑色纸板中也印上阿卡丽的图案，同样也做了光影处理来提升质感。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372204" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00900.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2002" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00900.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00900-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00900-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00900-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>纸板打开后，露出了位于手表两侧的快速说明书和阿卡丽替换表带，快速说明书下方则是手表充电器，这就是包装盒内所有的内容了。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372205" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00938.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00938.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00938-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00938-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00938-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>OPPO Watch 英雄联盟限定版本体还是做了不少定制设计的 ，开机后就能阿卡丽专属的表盘设计了，同时左右滑动还能切换其他阿卡丽定制表盘。</p>
<h3>最后和定价</h3>
<p>联名已经成为了手机厂商们最常见的产品策略了，最初和各大汽车厂商联名，设计和配置都和普通版本做出了区分，从厂商的角度而言是为了拉升品牌定位，这部分从联名版的定价就可以看出。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372206" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00965.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00965.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00965-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00965-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00965-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>而后与知名设计师、知名影视和知名游戏 IP 联名，则更多的是借用 IP 的影响力，拉进与用户的距离，扩大品牌影响力。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372207" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01001.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01001.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01001-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01001-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC01001-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>但对于用户而言，始终还是要看综合产品力，除了基础的配置外，设计以及和 IP 的定制做好不好，用不用心，才是真正能打动用户的原因。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1372208" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00962.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2001" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00962.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00962-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00962-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC00962-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>从社交媒体以及我周边英雄联盟玩家的惊呼等反馈来看，大家对此次限定版的用心程度还是予以了肯定，就是能不能成为限量 3000 套购买者之一的问题了。</p>
<p>最后说下售价的发售日期：</p>
<ul>
<li>OPPO Find X2 英雄联盟 S10 限定版售价为 4999 元， 10 月 19 日 21 点开售，限量 3000 套。</li>
<li>OPPO Watch 英雄联盟限定版售价为 1999 元，11 月 1 日正式开售。 ​​​​</li>
</ul>